    "The existing literature primarily discusses two approaches for LDCT image enhancement.",
    "The results for this section is provided in Table 5.",
    "Some methods focus on direct image translation from LDCT to full-dose CT (FDCT), while others involve a two-step process.",
    "In the latter approach, DL is utilized to restore the sinogram, followed by image reconstruction using Filtered Back Projection (FBP).",
    "The proposed method by Dong et al."
